Interpretation
--------------
This file is a DIY point-in-time approximation based on Wikipedia's current S&P 500 constituents and selected change table.
It reduces recency/survivorship bias versus a static current ticker list, but it is not institutional constituent history.
Remaining limitations: missing delisted price histories, ticker changes, mergers, corporate actions and delisting returns.